#Cration du model
In [13]:
num_classes = len(class_names)
model_CNN=keras.models. Sequential()

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Rescaling(1./255, input_shape=(img_height, img_width, 3)))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Conv2D(16, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.MaxPooling2D())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Conv2D(32, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.MaxPooling2D())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.MaxPooling2D())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dropout(0.5))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Flatten())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dense(128,activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dense(num_classes))

keras.utils.plot_model(model_CNN, show_shapes=True)

num_classes = len(class_names)
model_CNN=keras.models. Sequential()

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Rescaling(1./255, input_shape=(img_height, img_width, 3)))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Conv2D(16, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.MaxPooling2D())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))

model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Conv2D(32, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'))
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.MaxPooling2D())
model_CNN.add(keras.layers.Dropout(0.2))

In [60]:
for i in range(cm.shape[0]):
  TP= cm.iloc[i,i]
  FP=cm.iloc[i,:].sum()-TP
  FN=cm.iloc[:,i].sum()-TP
  TN=cm.sum().sum()-TP-FP-FN
  accuracy=(TP+TN)/cm.sum().sum()
  precision=TP/(TP+FP)
  recall=TP/(TP+FN)
  F1_Score=(2*precision*recall)/(precision+recall)
  print("les resultats de la classe",cm.index[i],"\n")
  print("accuracy=",+accuracy)
  print("precision=",+precision)
  print("recall=",+recall)
  print("F1_Score=",+F1_Score)
  print("\n")
